{"tid":428622,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖拍到終日都唔開心 如何","createTime":"2017-10-08T08:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T09:44:24.000Z","uid":130814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c013b48a5644c17b3b9ea559d22048b368e3bfbb","tid":428622,"uid":130814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"拍咗不少年<br />\n當然都經歷唔少吵架、甚至分手<br />\n但我咁多年一直堅持<br />\n永遠就係我讓步<br />\n<br />\n對方對我有嘢唔滿意<br />\n我即刻想辦法去改<br />\n我對對方有嘢唔滿意<br />\n佢就覺得點解要佢改<br />\n佢覺得冇問題 從不讓步<br />\n咁我就自己終日都好失意咁<br />\n即使直接同佢講<br />\n佢都冇咩動搖又直情唔想聽<br />\n<br />\n其實拍咁多年<br />\n95%都係我讓步我就佢<br />\n漸漸佢做好多嘢都會令我唔開心<br />\n如果拍拖拍到咁<br />\n係咪即係唔夾呢"},{"pid":"1ab7b6ea79cde4e2302cb41c8203f5cccd9acb25","tid":428622,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"你諗下對一世都係咁"},{"pid":"1032fa7e883bcaf82411d7db52e30695e7e95a9a","tid":428622,"uid":130814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T08:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你諗下對一世都係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6733e580d93f21ee8e4fa300039b3d19109e06ca","tid":428622,"uid":52949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"唔岩 咪唔好拍囉<br />\n男人唔係一定要有女ge<br />\n<br />\n有錢就得"},{"pid":"97f9869229ee5eec859fcf7cb29f73cc88889d25","tid":428622,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T09:00:43.000Z","msg":"拍咗不少年"},{"pid":"b88c3cd6e9346e0412e0feb028ec4475a98f30bf","tid":428622,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"食慣左屎 就唔覺得臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一係分手 ，一係繼續食屎"},{"pid":"793c172ab33d67b95e08981876c7cf95f0a6b516","tid":428622,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T09:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食慣左屎 就唔覺得臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cla